@access_token = 여기에 입력

### 게시글 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts
Authorization: {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "memberId": 1,
  "type": "인증",
  "title": "오늘의 스터디2",
  "content": {
    "textContent": "자료구조 스터디 완료",
    "imageUrls": [
      "https://storage.com/aaa.jpg",
      "https://storage.com/bbb.jpg"
    ]
  }
}


### 댓글 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/api/posts/1/comments
Authorization: {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "이것은 댓글 내용입니다.",
  "isSecret": false
}


### 댓글 조회 (최신순 정렬)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/posts/1/comments
Authorization: {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json


### 댓글 수정 (전체)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/posts/comments/1
Authorization: {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "1",
  "isSecret": false
}


### 댓글 수정 (일부)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/posts/comments/1
Authorization: {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isSecret": "true"
}


### 댓글 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/posts/comments/2
Authorization: {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json